description: When Shaw first saw Brock, he immediately got nervous looking at those bulging muscles of his, even though his body is also very impressive. “The guy works out! He’s…I mean, he works out!” Little did Shaw know, Brock requested him because he was as equally as impressed with his amazing body. Two muscles studs admiring each other is definitely hot. Two muscles studs in action together is even hotter!
title: Brock & Shaw: Bareback
